SUBSTANTIALLY ALL OF THE COMPANYS UNDISTRIBUTED INTERNATIONAL EARNINGS INTENDED TO BE INDEFINITELY REINVESTED IN OPERATIONS OUTSIDE THE U.S. WERE GENERATED BY SUBSIDIARIES ORGANIZED IN IRELAND, WHICH HAS A STATUTORY TAX RATE OF 12.5%. AS OF

